headline.print_headline: How Deep Can a Fish Go? Scientists May Have Answer
headline.main: How Deep Can a Fish Go? Scientists May Have Answer

lead_paragraph: They may look like guts stuffed in cellophane, but five fish hauled up from near-record depths off the coast of New Zealand are providing scientists with new insights into how deep fish can survive.
